Collplant Approved for Diabetes Injuries Human Clinical Study

-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 
2011-10-10T06:53:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/collplant-approved-for-diabetes-injuries-human-clinical-study.html
Collplant Holdings Ltd. (CLPT)  said its
unit received necessary permits to undertake together Israeli
health provider Maccabi Health Services a first human clinical
study for the treatment of chronic diabetic injuries with its
Vergenix bandages, the biotechnology company said in a statement
to the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Calev Ben-David at 
 cbendavid@bloomberg.net  